{"tid":818404,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"影視紅人屎萊姆拍完MVpost感性感謝文","createTime":"2018-09-14T05:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T06:31:17.000Z","uid":165934,"like":1,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2f736d72201d12eeed6735a34c3a3a3920e5696f","tid":818404,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:35:33.000Z","msg":"拍個MV，幕後功臣有咁多人☺️ #仲要未齊人 #以下長文 #慎入<br />\n.<br />\n因為我的任性，同我合作的人都好辛苦，有時因為唔滿意一個shot，明明OT緊都死要take 20-30次...大家勁攰都要死頂，忍受我嘅脾氣。能夠有大家幫手，真係好大福氣，挨義氣挨眼訓仲要病埋，呢個人情我真係唔識還...<br />\n.<br />\n有時好想做好件事，自己能力又唔夠...迫得自己好緊，一次要比一次好，想要進步，想要突破，但卡關時會好失落好難過，覺得自己handle唔到。<br />\n.<br />\n有時候會好lost唔知為左乜，因為責任繼續做落去，失去目標係一件非常可怕嘅事，會無動力，會求期，會想逃避，但大家的落力會令我重新振作！<br />\n.<br />\n擔心玩太大，擔心辛苦出黎成果唔好，擔心拖大家落水大家好難受，擔心有人受委屈，擔心安排唔好，擔心out bud，兩次MV拍完個一刻都極崩潰，心理質素還需要繼續磨練，希望帶大家走到更高更遠。<br />\n.<br />\n經歷呢兩次，大家就係兄弟姊妹，有咩用得著小弟嘅地方，即管開聲，火裡火裡去！<br />\n.<br />\n📸Photo by SoulPhotography<br />\n🍲Dinner at 浜滝 Hamataki <br />\n#獻醜 #獻醜之後<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/14/133416_229b2d305dcb9c58c80fd1c20f1be8e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2F133416_229b2d305dcb9c58c80fd1c20f1be8e0.png&h=732812f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿屎你辛苦了！！！你的任性都只是為了拍一個完美的MV給你的fans!我們明白的！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n永遠支持你喔阿屎！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5027dd0dcd9bd4f64cdf7287a71dc49ace401bb4","tid":818404,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:47:28.000Z","msg":"負評的人是甚麼心態！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e00ad770062e02d95b7bd8572d0d842ef178f7","tid":818404,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:56:37.000Z","msg":"睇完咸到收唔到聲😭😭"},{"pid":"d1a3c64084c2c5901b26644ea58965f3c850dd2b","tid":818404,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"28e00ad770062e02d95b7bd8572d0d842ef178f7","tid":818404,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:56:37.000Z","msg":"睇完咸到收唔到聲😭😭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:17:24.000Z","msg":"我都係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e6e6b3290cf61b7019cfa32def0eb343a7daa4","tid":818404,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:18:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56eda077c213d69523d16f10117d5f6b02160ca2","tid":818404,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ebc8b4d1c1902f83bce11382ff8633e8902672","tid":818404,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"28e00ad770062e02d95b7bd8572d0d842ef178f7","tid":818404,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:56:37.000Z","msg":"睇完咸到收唔到聲😭😭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"負皮係咩心態？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}